Question: What kind of cooking utensil has the same color as the pot?

Reference Answer: The spatula is the same color as the pot.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/2401498.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='pot')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What color is the pot?')
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='cooking utensil')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color is the cooking utensil?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'spoon' if {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} else 'other'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
